Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,东西都带全了吗\N{\rENG}So you got everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,你打算在飞机上一直玩游戏\N{\rENG}You gonna play video games all flight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:37.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,还是打算真的看会书\N{\rENG}or do you think you might actually crack open a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:39.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,大概会看会书\N{\rENG}Probably read some.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:43.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,别害怕给我回邮件 好吗\N{\rENG}If I write you an e-mail, don't be scared to write me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,让老爸了解下你的想法和近况\N{\rENG}Ok? It won't kill you to let your old man know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,又不会要了你的命\N{\rENG}what you're thinking about or what is going on, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,你愿意的话\N{\rENG}If you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:51.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们每周可以用网络电话聊聊天\N{\rENG}we can try Skyping once a week or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:52.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,自然科学课画的那些图纸带了吗\N{\rENG}You got the drawings for your science deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 应该带了  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- Yeah. I think so.  - Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你做得很好 真的特别棒\N{\rENG}Well, they turned out great by the way, like really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:01.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:04.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你的电脑充好电了吗  - 充好了\N{\rENG}- Is your computer charged?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:10.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,等你到家以后\N{\rENG}What do you think is the first thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:11.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你第一件要做的事是什么\N{\rENG}you are going to do when you get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:14.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很珍惜咱们这次交流的机会\N{\rENG}I really cherish this communication we have, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:21.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 只是你的回答都有点…  - 怎么了\N{\rENG}- It's just... your answers are so...  - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,坚持练习弹钢琴 好吗\N{\rENG}Just keep practicing the piano, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:24.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,你弹得很棒\N{\rENG}You're really good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:26.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且你都费了那么大功夫了\N{\rENG}and they spend so much time at that school of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,别忘了音乐这东西\N{\rENG}Just... just remember that music is actually something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:30.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,会有助于你的生活\N{\rENG}that you'll use in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,别忘了…你要芝麻味的 对吧\N{\rENG}Don't forget to... you want those sesame things right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:33.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,那种特好吃\N{\rENG}They're really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:34.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:35.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Γεια σου!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:43.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我大概十月能过去\N{\rENG}I probably make it over there in October.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:44.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会尽量赶去看你的第一次独奏\N{\rENG}I'll try to see you in that first recital
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:46.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,最好还能赶上看你踢场球赛\N{\rENG}and hopefully catch a soccer game while I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:50.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rENG}Ευχαριστώ!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,今年我可能不会再踢足球了\N{\rENG}I might not even play soccer this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:56.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,这绝对是个错误的决定 相信我\N{\rENG}That would be a big mistake, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:58.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我踢得不好\N{\rENG}I'm not that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 你踢得很好 非常好\N{\rENG}Oh no, you're pretty good, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:03.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,可是…我错过了夏季训练营\N{\rENG}I mean... I missed summer training camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:06.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以不太可能让我回去了\N{\rENG}so the chances of me starting are miniscule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:08.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,你直接告诉教练你的情况\N{\rENG}Yes, well, just tell the coach your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你爸爸住在欧洲 你其实特想去\N{\rENG}Your dad lives in Europe and you really wanted to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是之类的借口 把责任推给我\N{\rENG}You know... blah, blah, blame me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我父母太讨厌了 但是我很上心的\N{\rENG}my parents stink but I'm really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我没那么上心 爸爸\N{\rENG}But I'm not serious, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是很在意那个\N{\rENG}I don't care that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:24.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,你也不用现在就做决定 多考虑考虑\N{\rENG}Well, you don't have to decide right now, just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:26.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就是觉得团队运动很重要\N{\rENG}All I'm saying is that team sports are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,就到这儿了\N{\rENG}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个机场 你呢\N{\rENG}I love this airport, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,这里太酷了\N{\rENG}It's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:37.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,是吧 我也觉得很酷\N{\rENG}Yeah, I know it's cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:38.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,要见到你妈妈了 兴奋吗\N{\rENG}Are you excited about seeing your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是啊 还有我的伙伴们  - 没错\N{\rENG}- Yeah, and all my friends.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:42.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的登机牌和护照都带了吗\N{\rENG}What about your boarding pass, passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 转机你没问题吧\N{\rENG}Ok... Do you feel confident about making the connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:46.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 我以前都是这样的\N{\rENG}Yes, I have done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:49.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,但这次有点复杂\N{\rENG}Yes, but this is a tricky connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:52.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,飞机着陆后 记着坐着别起来\N{\rENG}Just remember that when you land you stay in your seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,会有航空公司的人来接你\N{\rENG}somebody from the airline is going to come get you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:54.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你带去登机口\N{\rENG}and take you to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,记住了吗\N{\rENG}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没问题的  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- It's not a problem.  - Ok, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,伙计\N{\rENG}Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:06.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,看来真的得说再见了 是吧\N{\rENG}Well... it looks like maybe we should just do this thing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:10.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,过来 天啊\N{\rENG}Ok, come here! Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:12.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,我会尽量赶去看你独奏的 好吗\N{\rENG}I'll do my best to make that recital, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.95,0:03:16.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实…我不介意的\N{\rENG}You know... I wouldn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,为什么这么说\N{\rENG}What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是故意要刻薄你\N{\rENG}Look, I'm not being mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,但如果你不来看我独奏的话我会更轻松\N{\rENG}but it would be easier if you didn't come to the recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么会呢\N{\rENG}How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:27.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你选别的周末来看我更好\N{\rENG}It would just be better if you visited on a nothing weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想看你弹琴\N{\rENG}I want to see you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是妈妈真的很讨厌你\N{\rENG}Look. It's because mom hates you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:33.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你在 她会特别紧张\N{\rENG}She would be really stressed if you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,弄得我也很有压力\N{\rENG}and then it would be tense for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你知道吗  - 谢谢\N{\rENG}- You know...  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且咱们也没有时间一起玩\N{\rENG}We wouldn't have any time to hang out anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,别担心 会有办法的\N{\rENG}Do not worry about it, we'll figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不希望你担心这个 好吗\N{\rENG}I just don't want you to worry about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:51.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多想你 对吧\N{\rENG}I mean... You know how much I miss you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你为什么觉得她还那么讨厌我\N{\rENG}Why do you think she still hates me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:58.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得相比起来她更讨厌丹尼尔一些\N{\rENG}I think she hates Daniel more than she hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:02.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,别担心 我会想办法的\N{\rENG}Hey, don't worry about it, I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我该进去了\N{\rENG}We should just do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 还有什么我能帮忙的吗\N{\rENG}Yeah, but is there anything I can do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:13.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 但是你知道我爱你 对吗  - 当然\N{\rENG}- But you know that I love you, right?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,我当然知道 这是我过得最好的一个夏天\N{\rENG}Yeah, I know! This has been the best summer of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 真的吗  - 真的\N{\rENG}- Really?  - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也这么想 看吧\N{\rENG}For me too, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我就说过希腊会是个特别棒的地方\N{\rENG}I told you, this whole Greece thing was going to be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,确实是\N{\rENG}And it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:26.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爱你 伙计\N{\rENG}Ok! I love you, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:27.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也爱你 爸爸\N{\rENG}I love you too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,来 握个手\N{\rENG}Ok... shake my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:31.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rENG}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:38.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 好的\N{\rENG}Oui, oui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,他跟德国人有个合作项目\N{\rENG}Il a un projet avec les Allemands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,像往常一样\N{\rENG}Comme d'habitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:06:02.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\b1\fsp20\shad0\c&H296863&}卡拉玛塔机场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:06.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,听我说 会议气氛太压抑了\N{\rENG}écoutez, on est stressé en cette réunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 不 我是说下周\N{\rENG}Non, bah, non. La semaine prochaine j'ai dit oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:12.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs65\fsp10\fscx150\shad2\4a&H33&\pos(985,895)}爱在午夜降临前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 那太好了\N{\rENG}Ok, bon, très bien.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢 您也一样 再见\N{\rENG}Merci, oui, oui, vous aussi hein. Au revoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我被排除在外了\N{\rENG}Ah, j'suis débusquée.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 他们投票反对\N{\rENG}- What's going on?  - They voted against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,反对什么 安装风力涡轮机吗\N{\rENG}What? The wind turbines?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,和这些人打了六个月的交道\N{\rENG}6 months dealing with these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:31.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,好不容易都同意了\N{\rENG}they were all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,大家都认为这对地区有好处\N{\rENG}Everyone agreed it was great for the region.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,那出什么岔子了\N{\rENG}So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在他们都觉得涡轮机\N{\rENG}Now they've decided that they don't like the way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:36.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,放在山上的样子不好看\N{\rENG}that it looks on that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:37.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们说那样有碍观瞻\N{\rENG}It's "Ruining their view."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:38.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,这件事不是都定下来了吗\N{\rENG}I thought it was a done deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 当时都说定了\N{\rENG}It was! It practically was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,那他们怎么还能这么做\N{\rENG}Can they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然 他们就这么做了 这事儿完了\N{\rENG}Of course! They've done it, and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:47.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,没事 我只是太沮丧了\N{\rENG}No, no, it's so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我忍不下去了\N{\rENG}I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要接海米尔那活了\N{\rENG}I'm gonna take that job with Hemir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,别 你不想为他们工作\N{\rENG}No, you do not wanna work for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 为政府工作吗\N{\rENG}- Why not?  - For the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得这届政府和以往不同\N{\rENG}I think this government is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们需要法律支持 这是唯一的办法\N{\rENG}We need laws and it's the only way anything is gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,总有别的法子的\N{\rENG}That's not the only way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,你们已经做了很多不错的工作了\N{\rENG}you guys have been getting a lot of good work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我考虑过了 只有这办法行得通\N{\rENG}Well, I've been thinking about it, this is the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 那你可别忘了\N{\rENG}Ok, well then let me remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,你和那人合不来\N{\rENG}that you do not like that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,以前你在他那工作的时候\N{\rENG}The whole time you worked for him before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:14.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你整天都在抱怨\N{\rENG}you complained about him constantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 他是个混蛋\N{\rENG}Yeah, yeah, yeah... He can be an asshole
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:16.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是他能帮我把事搞定\N{\rENG}but he gets things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,从现在开始我就得这么想了\N{\rENG}That's how I'm gonna be from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 我要做个贱人\N{\rENG}- Ok.  - A real bitch, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,每次我见他都觉得他是狼子野心\N{\rENG}Well, every time I look at that guy all I see is ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起 我就是不信任他\N{\rENG}I mean, I'm sorry, I don't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,他从非营利部门转入政府的唯一原因\N{\rENG}The only reason he's going from not for profit to government
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是想有人能拍他马屁\N{\rENG}is to have people kiss his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不在乎他怎么样 好吗\N{\rENG}I don't care about him, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就是觉得你会过得特痛苦\N{\rENG}Ok, I think you are gonna be miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,面对数不清的政治活动和协商会议\N{\rENG}With all the politicking and compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:35.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,无所谓\N{\rENG}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已经决定了\N{\rENG}I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.58,ZHU,,0,0,0,,典出{\u1}古希腊神话{\u0}中诸神对西西弗斯的惩罚，让他每每接近成功又前功尽弃\N{\rCHS}我不想再做把大石头推上山\N{\rENG}I'm tired of being the do-gooder who rolls a boulder up a hill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,再看着它滚下来的老好人了\N{\rENG}and watches it roll down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,他以前不是经常\N{\rENG}Wasn't he the guy who used to throw his pens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,扔笔砸他的助理吗\N{\rENG}at his assistants and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:46.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我一年前就该接这份工作了\N{\rENG}Ok, I should have taken this job a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,我害怕是因为工作量太大\N{\rENG}And I was scared because of the amount of work
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得这是个绝好的机会\N{\rENG}but I think it's the best opportunity ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,工资也更高 我决定了\N{\rENG}And it's more money, and I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你确定吗\N{\rENG}Ok, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:58.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,不确定 我什么都不确定 行吗\N{\rENG}No, I'm not sure of anything, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:02.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我走了 那其他人都怎么办\N{\rENG}I mean, what's gonna happen to everyone if I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,弗朗索瓦他们都指着我呢\N{\rENG}Like Francois... I mean, they count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢\N{\rENG}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:07.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我该不该接那个工作\N{\rENG}Should I take it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 不 我不发表意见\N{\rENG}Oh, no no no, I don't have an opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是不想你因为风力涡轮机的失败\N{\rENG}No, I just don't want to see you rush into a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,就匆忙做出决定\N{\rENG}because this wind turbine crap is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,不仅是因为那个 好吗\N{\rENG}It's not just that, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我都蠢蠢欲动一整个夏天了\N{\rENG}It's been stirring me all summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 不 我知道的  - 我要接这个工作 我决定了\N{\rENG}- No, I know it has, I know.  - I should do it. I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就接吧\N{\rENG}Then do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,我决定了 好吗\N{\rENG}I'm doing it! Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,上帝啊 我真希望事情都能简单些\N{\rENG}Oh God, I wish that things were simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我走也完蛋 我留也完蛋\N{\rENG}I mean... if I leave I get fucked, if I stay I get fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,永远都不确定\N{\rENG}It's always a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,没错 这就是个操蛋的世界\N{\rENG}Yeah, the world is fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得也是\N{\rENG}Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 好不容易能度个假期了\N{\rENG}Oh God, we finally have a vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,头两个星期姑娘们还生病了\N{\rENG}and the girls are sick for the first two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,有个完美儿子 却还住在一百万英里外\N{\rENG}With the perfect son who lives a million miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:43.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,或者是你毕生所爱\N{\rENG}Or the love of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,刮完胡子不知道清理下\N{\rENG}who can't clean up after himself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:46.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,还不肯学学怎么刮胡子\N{\rENG}or learn how to shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,谁说的\N{\rENG}Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是在说这的清洁队队长吧\N{\rENG}You're not talking about Captain Clean-up over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,清洁队队长\N{\rENG}Captain Clean-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,那个在行动中都失踪了好几年的人\N{\rENG}The one that's been missing in action all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,这时候你希望我说什么\N{\rENG}What did you expect at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\rENG}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧她们 太可爱了\N{\rENG}Oh look at them, they're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像连体婴儿似的\N{\rENG}They look like conjoined twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 我得给她们照张相\N{\rENG}Oh my God, I'm gonna take a picture of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾拉那个苹果吃完了吗\N{\rENG}Hey, did Ella finish that apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要从孩子嘴里抢食吃吗\N{\rENG}You're going to take food out of your child's mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- Yeah.  - Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,都变成棕色了\N{\rENG}This all brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,没关系 还有一块可以吃\N{\rENG}No no, there is a spot here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:30.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾拉 这是你爸爸偷你食物的证据\N{\rENG}Ella, this is evidence of your father stealing food from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管你变得贪食还是厌食\N{\rENG}If you become bulimic or anorexic,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,都不是我的错 别全怪你妈妈 好吗\N{\rENG}it's not my fault, don't blame it all on your mother, Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾拉 这是个家庭分享苹果\N{\rENG}Ella, this is a family apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在教她们分享的重要性\N{\rENG}I'm teaching them the value of sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,宝贝我爱你\N{\rENG}I love you, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,多甜蜜啊 姑娘们会比咱们还要深刻地\N{\rENG}Ahhh, so sweet, you girls will remember this vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,铭记着这次与众不同的假期\N{\rENG}very different than we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是肯定的\N{\rENG}That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,从我妈那里我就知道了\N{\rENG}I see that with my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,她对我童年的印象和我完全不同\N{\rENG}she remembers my childhood entirely different than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:52.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,别拍我了\N{\rENG}Please stop filming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:58.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,天啊 我爱你妈妈 你对她太苛刻了\N{\rENG}God. I love your mom, you're always so hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,因为你错过了那些操蛋的岁月\N{\rENG}It is because you missed the fucked-up years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:01.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,你赶上了好时候\N{\rENG}you are just getting the good era.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:03.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,操蛋的岁月\N{\rENG}The fucked-up years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,说到操蛋我想起来了\N{\rENG}That reminds me, talking about fucked-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你我那只艳后猫咪的事吗\N{\rENG}did I ever tell you the story about my little Cleopatra kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我记不得了 我要是说过你肯定有印象\N{\rENG}I dunno? Ok. I think you would remember if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,故事是这样的\N{\rENG}It's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:17.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,我小时候养了只猫 起名叫埃及艳后\N{\rENG}You know when I was a little girl I had this cat named Cleopatra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,每到春天她都会跳出栅栏然后怀孕\N{\rENG}And every spring she would jump the fence and get pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:25.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,每次都会生出恰好两只猫咪\N{\rENG}And always end up with a litter of exactly two kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:28.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 恰好两只  - 每次 每年都是两只\N{\rENG}- Two kitties.  - Every time, every year, two cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:32.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,很神奇 在我三十岁左右的某一天\N{\rENG}I mean... it's just amazing, then one days I was like around 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:36.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我和我爸爸一起吃午饭 回忆过去\N{\rENG}And I was having lunch with my dad and was remembering,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,提到了小埃及艳后\N{\rENG}mentioning little Cleopatra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:41.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,他说自己做过最艰难的事\N{\rENG}And he was like... the hardest thing I ever had to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:44.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,就是杀掉那些可爱的小猫咪\N{\rENG}was to kill those cute little kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我惊讶极了\N{\rENG}And I was like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:48.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 其实就是这么回事\N{\rENG}It turns out ... listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:52.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,有时她会一窝生出七只猫咪\N{\rENG}There was sometimes up to 7 kittens in that litter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我爸爸就拿走五只\N{\rENG}But he would take 5 of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,把它们放进一个塑料袋 然后灌乙醚\N{\rENG}put them in a plastic bag, with a bunch of ether.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,太可怕了\N{\rENG}That is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,就好像 他似乎忘记了\N{\rENG}That was like... He had forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,当初他和妈妈是怎么骗我的了\N{\rENG}the lie he and my mum had told me about the kittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,他怎么决定该杀哪几只呢\N{\rENG}How did he decide which ones he wanted to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:07.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,其实我倒真问过他\N{\rENG}Well actually I asked him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:11.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是拿走最毛茸茸的 最可爱的\N{\rENG}Did you take the, you know, the fluffiest, cutest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:15.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后他就开始哭 可怜的老爸\N{\rENG}You know, and he just started to cry, poor daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,咱们说过要在这里停车的\N{\rENG}Oh we said we would gonna stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,孩子们要看遗迹\N{\rENG}They wanted to see the ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 没错  - 艾拉特想看\N{\rENG}- Yeah.  - Well, Ella really wanted to ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 但是咱们该把她们叫醒吗\N{\rENG}Yes, but should we wake them up?
