Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.83,0:34:06.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,不会有那一天的\N{\rENG}That will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.05,0:34:09.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想现在唯一的问题是什么时候会发生\N{\rENG}I think the only question is when it's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.49,0:34:12.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想与卡斯特罗的感觉差不多\N{\rENG}I think I will probably feel about the same way as Kasparov
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.19,0:34:12.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,记得吧\N{\rENG}you remember, all those
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:14.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有那些棋手都不能战胜的\N{\rENG}chess players felt when they could no compete
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.55,0:34:15.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,超级电脑\N{\rENG}with that big-ass computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.55,0:34:16.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 深蓝  - 对对 就是那个\N{\rENG}- The big blue.  - Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.70,0:34:17.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,最初大家都认为\N{\rENG}Remember at first thought
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.69,0:34:19.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,电脑不能战胜人类\N{\rENG}nobody thought a computer could ever beat our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.74,0:34:24.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,机器没有人类那妙不可言的天资\N{\rENG}A machine lacks that ineffable human instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.45,0:34:27.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,现在我们却输得一塌糊涂\N{\rENG}You know and now we can't even compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.06,0:34:28.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看过一篇文章\N{\rENG}I saw a documentary where
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.06,0:34:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,上面说他们用小白鼠做了个实验\N{\rENG}they were doing an experiment on a lab rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.62,0:34:32.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,将它身上连了个开关\N{\rENG}And..he was wired up and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.59,0:34:35.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,打开开关它就能高潮\N{\rENG}could push a switch and have an orgasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.45,0:34:37.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,然后这个可怜的小家伙\N{\rENG}and so, the scientists were
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.67,0:34:40.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,让科学家们一顿爆笑\N{\rENG}sort of laughing at this pathetic little creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.26,0:34:44.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,它不吃不喝 就不停的触摸开关\N{\rENG}While it ignores food and water and didn't do anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.51,0:34:46.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后它就这么死了\N{\rENG}And eventually it just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.30,0:34:47.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我觉得这就是\N{\rENG}I mean, I think that's the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.48,0:34:49.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,人类的未来 就像…\N{\rENG}future of humanity, you know? Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.76,0:34:52.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,爽到死\N{\rENG}and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.58,0:34:55.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,有可能吧\N{\rENG}Well, maybe so
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.02,0:34:57.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,每代人都认为\N{\rENG}but every generation believes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.59,0:35:00.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,自己见证了世界末日\N{\rENG}that they're witnessing the end of the world.
