Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.23,0:40:33.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的丈夫有事吗 有其他人受伤吗\N{\rENG}How is my husband? Is anyone else hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.80,0:40:38.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,而男人们 无一例外\N{\rENG}Every man with no exception, when they
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.09,0:40:41.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,当他们被这样告知 第一反应是什么呢\N{\rENG}were told all this, what was the first thing they did?
