Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.10,0:40:55.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,最后\N{\rENG}Yeah, yeah, and eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.53,0:40:59.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们回过神来 才想起问问他们的孩子\N{\rENG}they come around to asking about their kids
