Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.22,0:54:01.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你真是疯了\N{\rENG}Ok... you're really crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.74,0:54:03.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是戈尔巴乔夫\N{\rENG}That was Gorbachev.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.13,0:54:05.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你这个地理不通\N{\rENG}Ok? Geographically challenged,
