Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.12,0:54:08.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是戈尔巴乔夫\N{\rENG}That was Gorbachev.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.91,0:54:11.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我总搞不清东方国家的这些领袖\N{\rENG}I'm sorry I got Eastern-bloc leaders mixed up, OK.
