Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.11,0:54:20.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以那是戈尔巴乔夫\N{\rENG}So was it Gorbachev?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.42,0:54:21.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你知道的\N{\rENG}All right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.07,0:54:25.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,听着 我本来打算一会儿再跟你说\N{\rENG}Listen to this... I was going to wait
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.81,0:54:29.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,可我这个人就是藏不住话\N{\rENG}to tell you this till later, but I'm so bad with secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.92,0:54:30.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.23,0:54:32.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,你脑子里长了肿瘤 快死了吗\N{\rENG}You've got a tumor in your brain and you are going to die?
