Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.70,0:54:37.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 其实也有点像\N{\rENG}Well, actually, it's kind of like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.32,0:54:40.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我祖母死了  - 不是吧 什么时候的事\N{\rENG}- My grandmother died.  - What! When?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.35,0:54:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 我们吃饭前我爸爸发短信告诉我的\N{\rENG}Yes, my dad texted to me right before we ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.00,0:54:45.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起 你怎么不早说\N{\rENG}Oh I'm so sorry. Why didn't you tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.35,0:54:46.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,像每个人都希望的那样\N{\rENG}Everyone has been expecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.93,0:54:48.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,她活得够长了 而且一生幸福\N{\rENG}she has lived a long time, had a great life.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.83,0:54:50.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,她九十六岁了\N{\rENG}She was 96.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.19,0:54:53.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,你祖父死后没多久 她就去世了\N{\rENG}She did not live much longer after your grandfather died.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.34,0:54:55.15,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 有一年了\N{\rENG}No... barely a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.17,0:54:58.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,有趣的是 这女人还是个奇怪的圣人\N{\rENG}The funny thing is that this woman was a freaking saint, ok?
