Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.72,0:55:31.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,靠 怎么可能\N{\rENG}Fuck! How is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.80,0:55:35.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是我们也一起生活七十四年 那得多老啊\N{\rENG}How old will we be if we were together for 74 years?
