Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.55,0:56:46.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,他告诉我说 我的祖父母\N{\rENG}Well... he told me that my grandparents
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.08,0:56:47.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,想要死后葬在一起\N{\rENG}wanted to have a joint service.
