Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.72,0:57:43.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 你还能再忍受我五十六年吗\N{\rENG}Well... will you be able to put up with me for 56 more years?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.91,0:57:47.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我也想知道  - 你又来了\N{\rENG}- I'm looking forward to it.  - Shit, you're really working it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.57,0:57:51.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,你性爱时的甘露就如同陈年美酒\N{\rENG}The nectar of your sex ages like a fine wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.43,0:57:54.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我长毛的西班牙小伙又变身希腊人了\N{\rENG}O-o, my hairy Spanish lover is back Greek,
