Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.74,0:58:01.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,这地方让我想起了\N{\rENG}Wow, this place reminds me
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.33,0:58:03.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,我小时候看过的一部电影\N{\rENG}a bit of a movie I saw when I was a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.81,0:58:06.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是一部五十年代的黑白片\N{\rENG}It was a black and white film from the 50s.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.94,0:58:09.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我记得 有一对夫妇走在庞贝古城的废墟旁\N{\rENG}I remember a couple walking through the ruins of Pompeii,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.74,0:58:12.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,看着那些在那里躺了好几个世纪的尸骸\N{\rENG}viewing bodies that had been lying there for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.76,0:58:14.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,我还记得那些尸骸\N{\rENG}I remember the bodies, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.48,0:58:17.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们在睡梦中被捕的时候还紧拥着爱人\N{\rENG}caught in their sleep still lovingly holding each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.35,0:58:21.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也不知道为什么 有时候我经常在想\N{\rENG}I don't know why, sometimes I have this image in my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.86,0:58:24.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,你搂着我 我们躺在一起\N{\rENG}where, you know, we're asleep and you hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.47,0:58:26.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,在炽热的灰烬下被活活掩埋\N{\rENG}What... of being buried alive under molten ash?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.65,0:58:28.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你就是在想这些吗  - 是的\N{\rENG}- That's what you're thinking about?  - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.70,0:58:30.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,这可一点都不好玩\N{\rENG}That's not very fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.42,0:58:33.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道 其实也没那么可怕\N{\rENG}I don't know... It's not horrible I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.63,0:58:36.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,他们当中 有些夫妇中间还躺着孩子\N{\rENG}they had some bodies with little kids sleeping between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.39,0:58:37.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,那很好\N{\rENG}That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.95,0:58:39.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 我想我年轻的时候有些病态\N{\rENG}Yeah, I guess I was young and a bit morbid,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.74,0:58:42.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,觉得和自己心爱的人死在一起是很浪漫的事\N{\rENG}I mean at that age you romanticize dying with the person you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.77,0:58:44.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,那现在你愿意和我一起死吗\N{\rENG}Now you want to die with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.88,0:58:47.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许吧 你知道 如果是\N{\rENG}Maybe you know if you were... you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.74,0:58:50.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在一起的第一个晚上 也许会\N{\rENG}our first night together then,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.01,0:58:52.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,可那是好久以前了 现在我才不\N{\rENG}a long time ago, but now... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.05,0:58:52.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想活着\N{\rENG}I'd like to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.97,0:58:55.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也只是想来点浪漫的 也被你破坏了\N{\rENG}I just wanted you to say something romantic and you blew it!
