Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.70,0:59:00.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,等我们都九十八岁了 你可以再问一次\N{\rENG}Ok, if we are both 98, you can ask me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.98,0:59:02.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,不过现在\N{\rENG}But any time sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.27,0:59:06.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起了\N{\rENG}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.34,0:59:08.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是我说过的那个拜占庭时期\N{\rENG}Hey... This is the chapel I was telling you about.
