Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.08,1:00:01.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,那会让整个国际社会为之一颤的\N{\rENG}That will send a shiver through international community.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.42,1:00:04.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 那我再也不给土耳其人吹箫了\N{\rENG}OK, fine. Then I will never suck another turkish cock.
