Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.54,1:00:09.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,那太糟糕了\N{\rENG}Oh that's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.30,1:00:11.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,我忘了你是个秘密修行的基督徒\N{\rENG}No! I forgot you're a closet-Christian.
