Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.40,1:00:38.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道她们为什么这么想要我们结婚\N{\rENG}I do not know why they want us to be married so badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.49,1:00:40.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,这对她们很重要\N{\rENG}It is important to them.
