Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.52,1:38:57.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你想我读给你听吗  - 我还有选择吗\N{\rENG}- Do you want me to read it to you?  - Do I have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.23,1:38:59.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,当然 如果你不感兴趣\N{\rENG}Sure. I mean, if you're not interested in...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.11,1:39:01.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,不不不 读吧\N{\rENG}No, no, no. Read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.36,1:39:05.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 听好了 亲爱的瑟琳\N{\rENG}OK. Here it is: Dear Celine,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.44,1:39:09.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我从森林另一边给你写信\N{\rENG}I am writing to you from the other side of the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.41,1:39:11.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,这封信会点燃\N{\rENG}This letter is lighting a candle...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.64,1:39:14.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,够了 我不会写这个的 太花哨\N{\rENG}OK, stop it. I would never write this, too flowery,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.26,1:39:15.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,“森林另一边” 什么森林\N{\rENG}"Other side of the woods"? What fucking woods?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.86,1:39:18.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你在说什么  - 我可以继续吗\N{\rENG}- What are you talking about?  - May I please continue?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.18,1:39:19.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Ok...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.23,1:39:22.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,我把这个年轻人派去你身边\N{\rENG}I'm sending you this young man,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.31,1:39:24.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 年轻人\N{\rENG}yes, young.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.10,1:39:26.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,他会是你的护卫\N{\rENG}And he will be your escort.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.92,1:39:29.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,天晓得他有多少毛病\N{\rENG}God knows he has many problems
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.20,1:39:32.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,他终其一生都在\N{\rENG}and he's struggled his whole life connecting
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.59,1:39:37.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,努力亲近陪伴他最爱的人\N{\rENG}and being present, even with those he loves the most.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.25,1:39:39.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,对此 他万分抱歉\N{\rENG}And, for that, he is deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.26,1:39:43.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是你是他唯一的希望\N{\rENG}But you are his only hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.80,1:39:45.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑟琳\N{\rENG}Celine,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.30,1:39:48.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我对你的建议是\N{\rENG}my advice to you is this:
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.39,1:39:51.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你已经进入人生中最美好的年华\N{\rENG}You're entering the best years of your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.06,1:39:54.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,从我这个年纪回望过去\N{\rENG}Looking back from where I sit now,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.89,1:39:59.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,这段中年岁月仅比你十二岁和马修·瓦内萨\N{\rENG}these middle years are only a little bit more difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.33,1:40:03.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,彻夜欢跳比吉斯的“你的爱有多深”\N{\rENG}than when you were 12 and Matthew and Vanessa
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.06,1:40:08.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,要艰难一些\N{\rENG}danced all night to the Bee Gees' "How deep is your love".
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.27,1:40:09.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不知道是什么\N{\rENG}I don't know what that...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.54,1:40:12.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,算了 瑟琳 你会没事的\N{\rENG}Anyway... Celine, you will be fine,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.86,1:40:15.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的女儿们会成长为\N{\rENG}your girls will grow up to become examples
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.36,1:40:18.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 女权运动的典范  - 不错\N{\rENG}- and icons of feminism.  - Nice one.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.39,1:40:20.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 我刚注意到\N{\rENG}Yeah. Well you know I just noticed that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.05,1:40:23.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,底下有一段附言\N{\rENG}there's a postscript on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.03,1:40:25.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,也许我应该跳过 这些太无聊了\N{\rENG}Maybe I just skip over, some of this is kind of boring...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.17,1:40:26.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 跳过 跳过\N{\rENG}Yes. Skip away, please, skip away.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.59,1:40:27.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 你确定  - 是\N{\rENG}- Ok... you sure?  - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.98,1:40:30.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 絮絮叨叨的\N{\rENG}- Alright, well...  - Boring stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.71,1:40:33.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,好的 下面就是说什么\N{\rENG}Ok... yeah, it's like blah blah blah,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.54,1:40:36.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,经济注意事项啦 星座啦\N{\rENG}financial tips, horoscopes...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.96,1:40:41.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,好了这里 附言 顺便说下\N{\rENG}Ok... Here it is: P.S. By the way...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.01,1:40:49.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,顺便说下 我一生中最棒的性体验\N{\rENG}By the way, the best sex of my life happened one night
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.26,1:40:51.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,是在伯罗奔尼撒南部的一夜\N{\rENG}in the Southern Peloponnese.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.19,1:40:53.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,别错过\N{\rENG}Don't miss it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.35,1:40:59.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的性福达到一个新的里程碑\N{\rENG}My whole sexual being went to a whole new ground-breaking level.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.27,1:41:01.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,新的里程碑 很好\N{\rENG}Ground-breaking, great.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.60,1:41:03.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 你知道这什么意思吗\N{\rENG}Yeah ... you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.12,1:41:05.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,杰西 能停止这个愚蠢的游戏吗\N{\rENG}Ok. Jesse. Can you stop this stupid game?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.38,1:41:08.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们不是你小说里的人物\N{\rENG}We're not in one of your stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.39,1:41:09.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\rENG}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.33,1:41:12.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,你听到我返回房间说的话吗\N{\rENG}Did you hear what I said to you back in the room?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.73,1:41:13.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,你听到了吗\N{\rENG}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.23,1:41:16.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.37,1:41:17.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,听到了\N{\rENG}I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.01,1:41:20.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不爱我了吗\N{\rENG}What, that you don't love me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.29,1:41:24.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,我以为你不是那意思 但如果你就是那意思\N{\rENG}I figured you didn't mean it but if you did then...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.67,1:41:28.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rENG}Oh, fuck it, you know something?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.83,1:41:30.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,你就像个小女孩\N{\rENG}You're just like the little girls
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.09,1:41:33.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,希望周围的人都生活在童话中\N{\rENG}and everybody else you want to live inside some fairy tale, alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.23,1:41:35.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我来这是想挽回 好吗\N{\rENG}I'm just trying to make things better here, alright?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.65,1:41:37.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你我无条件爱你\N{\rENG}I tell you that I love you unconditionally,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.35,1:41:38.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你你很美\N{\rENG}I tell you that you're beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.49,1:41:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告诉你你的屁股八十岁都风采依旧\N{\rENG}I tell you that your ass looks great when you're 80
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.26,1:41:46.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我努力想逗你笑  - 好吧\N{\rENG}- I'm trying to make you laugh.  - Ok
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.82,1:41:49.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,我忍受你一大堆臭脾气\N{\rENG}I've put up with plenty of your shit
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.14,1:41:52.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你以为我是条狗 总是回来找你\N{\rENG}and if you think I'm just some dog who's gonna keep coming back,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.70,1:41:58.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你错了 但如果你想要真爱 这就是爱\N{\rENG}then you're wrong. But if you want true love then this is it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.61,1:42:01.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是生活 不完美但很真实\N{\rENG}This is real life. It's not perfect but it's real,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.59,1:42:03.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你看不到 那是你瞎了\N{\rENG}and if you can not see it then you're blind.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.77,1:42:05.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吗 我放弃\N{\rENG}Alright? I give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.90,1:42:45.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,时光机是什么样的\N{\rENG}So what about this time machine?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.68,1:42:50.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你什么意思\N{\rENG}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.73,1:42:52.95,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么工作的\N{\rENG}How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.40,1:42:56.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,很复杂\N{\rENG}Well, it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.32,1:43:03.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,操作时要光着身子吗\N{\rENG}Am I gonna have to get naked to operate it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.08,1:43:11.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 我是说  - 是的 真是这样\N{\rENG}- I mean...  - Yeah, it's actually, it's been a real issue.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.20,1:43:13.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是说不穿…衣服\N{\rENG}I mean, I don't...clothes,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.90,1:43:16.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,不能顺利通过时空统一体\N{\rENG}they just don't travel well through whole space-time continuum.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.30,1:43:22.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇哦 你真聪明\N{\rENG}Wow, you're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.66,1:43:26.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,- Jesus  - 时空\N{\rENG}- Jesus.  - Space-time?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.25,1:43:30.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,- 统一体  - 统一体\N{\rENG}- Continuum.  - Continuum?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.20,1:43:31.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.92,1:43:36.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道我在想着你这封信\N{\rENG}You know something I've been thinking about your letter...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.28,1:43:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说你在伯罗奔尼撒南部住过\N{\rENG}You know you... you lived in the Southern Peloponnese?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.94,1:43:45.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我们就在伯罗奔尼撒南部\N{\rENG}Yeah, yeah and... we are in the Southern Peloponnese.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.46,1:43:49.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,你说今晚会不会就是你八十岁时\N{\rENG}And do you think it could be tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.04,1:43:51.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,依旧念念不忘的夜晚\N{\rENG}that you are still talking about in your 80s?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.77,1:43:53.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\rENG}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.72,1:43:58.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,今晚肯定会是个美妙的夜晚\N{\rENG}It was definitely one hell of a night we were about to have...
